---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<header class="gap-0 bg-white md:grid l:grid-cols-2">
	<div class="sticky flex items-center justify-center visual md:h-screen sm:relative md:top-0">
		<!-- <div class="z-10 w-1/2 animation aspect-square"></div> -->
		<img class="z-10 centered" src="../assets/images/logo-jdr-02-outline.svg" />
		<img
			class="absolute top-0 z-10 object-cover w-full h-full mix-blend-multiply"
			src="./assets/images/portret-jeff-halftone.png"
			alt="Jeff"
		/>
		<video class="z-5" src="../assets/video/03-test.mp4" autoplay loop playsinline muted></video>
	</div>

	<div class="item intro p-vw-8 pt-vw-32 pb-vw-12">
		<p class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight tw">
			I'm a dedicated film producer fueled by a passion for bringing compelling stories to the
			screen. I thrive on diverse storytelling methods, welcoming every avenue that leads to
			inspiration.
		</p>
		<p class="text-2xl mt-vw-8 tw">
			In film production, I turn creative ideas into impactful narratives. From consultancy to
			full-scale production, I specialize in documentaries, commercials, and films, overseeing
			projects from concept to completion.
		</p>
		<p class="text-1xl mt-vw-8 tw">
			Ready to bring your vision to life? Contact me for consultations, concepts, and collaboration.
			Email me anytime to kickstart our creative journey!
			<a href="https://www.instagram.com/jeffreyderoode/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">peek!</a>
		</p>
	</div>
</header>

<style>
	header {
		position: relative;
		background: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		min-height: 100vh;
		z-index: 10;
		transition:
			color var(--theme-transition),
			background var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.visual {
		background: var(--bg);
		z-index: 10;
		min-height: 50vh;
		transition:
			color var(--theme-transition),
			background var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.animation {
		background: url(./assets/images/logo-jdr-sprite.svg) no-repeat 0 0;
		background-size: 100%;
		animation: sprite 0.5s steps(4) infinite;
		/* z-index: 2; */
	}

	@keyframes sprite {
		from {
			background-position: 0 0;
		}
		to {
			background-position: 0 100%;
		}
	}

	video {
		object-fit: cover;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		opacity: 0.9;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.centered {
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		text-align: center;
		height: 60%;
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		header {
			min-height: 100vh;
			grid-template-rows: 1fr;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
